Hair Designer Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy governs the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data of users of the chatbot
Hair Designer
, developed by Mine Nur Kasımoğulları. We attach great importance to the protection of your privacy and are committed to processing your personal data in accordance with French law and the strictest privacy standards. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully before using our service. By using
Hair Designer
, you accept the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
1. Collection and Use of Personal Data
1.1. When you use
Hair Designer
, we may collect certain types of personal data about you, such as your name, email address, profile information, and conversation history. We collect this data for the purpose of providing you with a personalized experience and improving our services.
1.2. We may also collect technical data, such as information about your device, IP address, log files, and cookies, to facilitate your use of
Hair Designer
, and analyze usage trends.
2. Protection and Storage of Personal Data
2.1. We take appropriate security measures to protect your personal data against unauthorized access, loss, alteration, or disclosure. We use encryption methods and advanced security protocols to ensure the confidentiality of your data.
2.2. Your personal data will be retained for the duration necessary for the purposes mentioned in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.
3. Sharing of Personal Data
3.1. We may share your personal data with third parties in the following cases:
a) When necessary to provide our services and respond to your requests.
b) When required by law, a court order, or a request from a competent government authority.
c) With your prior consent.
4. Face Data
4.1.
Our app collects images containing facial data when you use the photo upload feature.
The face data is used solely to provide hair styling and color change features.
4.2. The face data is not shared with any third parties and is processed locally on your device.
4.3.It is not retained beyond the session and is discarded immediately after use.
5. Cookies and Similar Technologies
5
.1. We use cookies and other similar technologies to enhance your user experience, analyze usage trends, and personalize our service. You can configure your browser to refuse cookies, but this may limit certain features of
Hair Designer
.
6. Links to Third-Party Sites
6
.1.
Hair Designer
may contain links to third-party websites. This Privacy Policy does not apply to those sites. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of those third-party sites before providing your personal data.
7. Modification of the Privacy Policy
7
.1. We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. The modifications will take effect upon their publication on our website or
Hair Designer
. We encourage you to regularly review this Privacy Policy to stay informed of any updates.
8. Subscription Terms and End-User License Agreement (EULA)
8
.1.
Hair Designer
may offer paid subscriptions or in-app purchases. The details of these offerings, including pricing, payment methods, subscription duration, and terms and conditions, will be clearly communicated to the User within the application and governed by the End-User License Agreement (EULA). By subscribing or making in-app purchases, you agree to be bound by the terms and conditions specified in the EULA.
9.Contact
9
.1. If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at minekasimogullari@gmail.com
